# Customer Master UI Polish & Data Validation

Enhancing the Customer Master module by merging fragmented transactions, removing "Rp" currency prefixes, and converting static phone numbers into interactive WhatsApp actions.

## User Action Required

> [!NOTE]
> Review the new deduplication logic. We will merge all transactions based strictly on the **Customer Name**. If a customer has blank phone numbers in some transactions but valid phone numbers in others, their Total Spend (LTV) will be successfully united under one profile, taking their most recent valid phone number.

## Phase 21: Live Time & Top Advisor Serverless Migration

The goal is to sever the final two Google Sheets dependencies driving the heavy analytic menus: Live Time Matrix and Top Advisor. 

### Proposed Changes

#### 1. Live Time Matrix ([8-API_LiveTime.gs](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/CRM-APP/8-API_LiveTime.gs))
Currently, `buildLiveTimeExtraction` iterates through arrays of the entire database to calculate lifetime aggregates across 12 months.
- **Refactor `buildLiveTimeExtraction()`**: Replace `SpreadsheetApp.openById` logic with `Supabase.get` REST calls.
  - Pull `transaction_date`, `location`, `prospect_item` from `mirror_traffic`.
  - Pull `tanggal_input`, `lokasi_store` from `mirror_profiling`.
- **Note**: The API will still save the final aggregated small output to `LIVE_SHEET_NAME` to act as cache layer, maintaining ultra-fast UI load times via [getLiveTimeDashboardData()](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/CRM-APP/8-API_LiveTime.gs#6-81).

#### 2. Top Advisor Module ([9-API_Advisor.gs](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/CRM-APP/9-API_Advisor.gs))
Currently, [getTopAdvisorPerformance](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/CRM-APP/9-API_Advisor.gs#6-114) loops through Traffic and Profiling extracting advisor metrics.
- **Refactor [getTopAdvisorPerformance()](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/CRM-APP/9-API_Advisor.gs#6-114)**: Retrieve data concurrently via `Supabase.get` with date filters or memory filters.
  - Traffic: `transaction_date`, `served_by`, `prospect_item`, `status`.
  - Profiling: `tanggal_input`, `customer_advisor`. Avoid the inefficient `rowStr.includes()` substring search by directly targeting the `customer_advisor` column inside `mirror_profiling`.

