## Phase 22: Outer Dashboard Serverless Migration

The dashboard analytics (Monthly View, Quarterly View, Daily Breakdown, BOD Report) currently iterate through the heavy `clean_master` Google Sheet, which scales poorly as the dataset grows. We will migrate all READ operations to the new Supabase `clean_master` table using a Facade pattern to minimize logic rewrites.

### Proposed Changes

#### 1. Supabase REST API Extension ([Supabase.gs](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/Supabase.gs))
- Add `SupabaseDB.getAllRows(table, query)` to support cursor/offset pagination, solving the default 1,000 row PostgREST limit and ensuring full datasets are safely pulled into memory.

#### 2. Data Facade Pattern ([6-Helpers.gs](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/6-Helpers.gs))
- Create standard adapter function `fetchSupabaseCleanMasterAs2DArray(year)` which executes `SupabaseDB.getAllRows`, maps the JSON Array back structurally into the 20-index array format previously provided by `SpreadsheetApp.getDataRange()`.
- Supports date filtering at the database layer `?transaction_date=gte...` to further trim API payload bloat.

#### 3. Deprecate `SpreadsheetApp` Reads
Substitute the `const data = cleanSheet.getDataRange().getValues()` stanza with `const data = fetchSupabaseCleanMasterAs2DArray(year)` in the following files:
- [MODIFY] [4-API_Dashboard.gs](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/4-API_Dashboard.gs) ([getDashboardData](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/4-API_Dashboard.gs#37-459), `getTopPerformers`, `getSapProjection`)
- [MODIFY] [5-API_Reports.gs](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/5-API_Reports.gs) ([getSapPerformance](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/5-API_Reports.gs#6-63), [getCategoryTrendData](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/5-API_Reports.gs#64-158), [getDetailedDailyData](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/5-API_Reports.gs#159-183) etc.)
- [MODIFY] [8-API_Quarterly.gs](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/8-API_Quarterly.gs) ([getQuarterlyData](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/8-API_Quarterly.gs#6-196), [getQuarterlyBudgetData](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/8-API_Quarterly.gs#372-520))
- [MODIFY] [10-API_Email.gs](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/10-API_Email.gs) (`getDailyEmailData`)
- [MODIFY] [11-API_BOD_Report.gs](file:///d:/Bvlgari%20Dashboard/11-API_BOD_Report.gs) (`getBODReportData`)

